{"tid":1477581,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"山齊士真正週薪係56萬鎊","createTime":"2019-08-16T07:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T04:56:47.000Z","uid":173952,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"29c3a0b0adc2673b7a2bfb96eba4dca242146710","tid":1477581,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:23:50.000Z","msg":"蘇帥想清洗山齊士<br />\n<br />\n  英國媒體的最新消息都稱，山齊士（A.Sanchez）想在今夏離開曼聯。曼聯方面也非常願意送走山齊士，但不得不面對的現實是，交易想要達成，曼聯或許不得不補貼山齊士的大部分工資才行。<br />\n<br />\n  來自《每日郵報》的消息稱，曼聯為山齊士支付的基本工資+肖像權+獎金+經理人費用等，總價算下來平均每週接近56萬鎊。雖然想要離隊，但是讓山齊士放棄這筆優厚的報酬幾乎是不可能的。<br />\n<br />\n  山齊士加盟曼聯後下滑明顯，如今沒有球隊願意為他支付高昂的轉會費，即便是租借，也沒有球隊願意匹配他如此高昂的週薪。因此，如果曼聯最終決定將他外租的話，肯定要補貼大部分的工資才行，也就勉勉強強能止個損。是否接受，就要看曼聯高層的決策了。"},{"pid":"594cd438bff1429f6305e4b7df0f5fba20b7f604","tid":1477581,"uid":173952,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:24:28.000Z","msg":"阿朗都係60萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"894bf05c9a52c3f483dae2016d6e06ff9def348e","tid":1477581,"uid":147001,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:30:58.000Z","msg":"今時今日仲有人信山神五十萬週薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd7c73bb4ad521712208f125d9b11508628f9be","tid":1477581,"uid":76310,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"894bf05c9a52c3f483dae2016d6e06ff9def348e","tid":1477581,"uid":147001,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:30:58.000Z","msg":"今時今日仲有人信山神五十萬週薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:13:29.000Z","msg":"56先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8efdb809d38a70355cd7e7b332c520827997098","tid":1477581,"uid":4180,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:27:48.000Z","msg"